data.description: Contract Pending. On the market for back up offers. Looking for space inside and out? Then this is the home for you! This PRE INSPECTED two story in Cottonwood Creek is updated and ready to move right in! Situated on an oversized lot with no back neighbors provides the privacy needed to enjoy the large patio entertaining space. The main floor and second floor both have updated LVP flooring for easy cleaning. Open floor plan main level has great flow with the rustic wood beams on the ceiling, updated tile fireplace, and beautifully updated kitchen with quartz countertops and tiled backsplash. Second floor boasts 4 spacious bedrooms and a primary suite with large walk-in closet and 3/4 en-suite bathroom that includes double sinks. Finished lower level is the perfect space for guests or another living space and includes loads of storage. This is a must see, so schedule your showing today!
